About:
Norwegian biorefinery Borregaard AS commits to reduce absolute scope 1 and 2 GHG emissions 53% by 2030 and 100% by 2050 from a 2009 base year.* Borregaard AS also commits to reduce absolute scope 3 GHG emissions by 30% by 2030 and 75% by 2050 from a 2017 base year.


*The target boundary includes biogenic emissions and removals associated with the use of bioenergy.


